{"tid":2075365,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中美角力】央視《人民日報》中新社《環時》 被美列「外國使團」嚴限運作","createTime":"2020-06-22T21:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T00:21:51.000Z","uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"81635bc1b36b75506ce153a972f3ecf766fcc88d","tid":2075365,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T21:15:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200623&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=61086159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200623%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D61086159&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7v2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=1f87606f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200623%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D61086159&h=874e9e11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200623&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=61086159</a><br />\n<br />\n【中美角力】央視《人民日報》中新社《環時》 被美列「外國使團」嚴限運作<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院周一將四間中國傳媒列為「外國使團」，包括中國中央電視台、中國新聞社（中新社）、《人民日報》、《環球時報》。<br />\n<br />\n國務院官員指該四媒體是中共喉舌，不應視之為普通外媒。主管東亞太平洋事務的美國助理國務卿史迪威（David Stilwell）表示，美國只是回應中方行動，指中國共產黨對該四個傳媒有全面「編輯控制」。他說，對歐盟及其他國家正考慮對中國媒體採取類似措施感到高興。<br />\n<br />\n被列「外國使團」後，該四媒體須向美國國務院提交在美工作人員的姓名、個人資料及人事變動，並向國務院登記在美租賃或持有的房產清單。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n全文請前往蘋果<br />\n支持蘋果！"},{"pid":"47e6802a03f8c7a61f5ad48cd7ec9c3508c7aa6c","tid":2075365,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T21:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba2aa4af363fab764f5e27789edeb68745bc111","tid":2075365,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T21:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"